<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<p><img src="/media/13103272/half-term-hero.jpg" alt="HalfTerm" data-udi="umb://media/9c140ee9b3344ab7b2217693a021dffb" /></p>
<p><strong>Have fun at half term</strong> - Half-Term as a family is especially great in our resorts as not only do our selected resorts offer child-friendly ski lessons, child-care, additional family friendly activities but also the days are a little brighter, sunnier and warmer so your little skiers have the ideal conditions to learn and improve. </p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/1e6f5e817a4f4af3b851984b9c3fa71c" href="/{localLink:umb://document/1e6f5e817a4f4af3b851984b9c3fa71c}" class="c-btn">View ski deals</a></p>
