<p> </p>
<h2>Best half-term resorts:</h2>
<p>We have put together a selection of resorts that offer the best of skiing, snowboarding and everything else you can enjoy on a winter holiday at half-term.</p>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h3 style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/bd152c97eb204c59a0ae4a5b65e2c1e5" href="/{localLink:umb://document/bd152c97eb204c59a0ae4a5b65e2c1e5}" title="France">France</a></h3>
<p><img src="/media/13082840/cande_stgm_mars018_0320.jpeg" alt="tignesskiarea" data-udi="umb://media/c14a28a609f646318f2b804c45ae0a1d" /></p>
<ul>
<li><span>Vast selection of slopes for beginners to advanced </span></li>
<li><span>Activities from horse riding, cinema to sledging</span></li>
<li><span>A large, in resort Wellness Centre &amp; Spa </span></li>
<li><span>High rated hotels and chalets</span></li>
<li><span>Free lift passes for children 8 years of age</span></li>
<li><span>Includes off-piste and snowparks</span></li>
<li><span>Well known for its good selection of restaurants</span></li>
<li><span>Popular for its gifts shops</span></li>
</ul>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/204ce8e4cf8c4ab09205501e16cb7565" href="/{localLink:umb://document/204ce8e4cf8c4ab09205501e16cb7565}" class="c-btn">View Tignes</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h3 style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/bd152c97eb204c59a0ae4a5b65e2c1e5" href="/{localLink:umb://document/bd152c97eb204c59a0ae4a5b65e2c1e5}" title="France">France</a> </h3>
<p><img src="/media/13103273/valdisere-527.jpg" alt="ValdIsere" data-udi="umb://media/d3bdffb088574423a386d56a6915fec8" /></p>
<ul>
<li>Wide variety of slopes for all abilities </li>
<li>Fantastic choice of chalets, hotels, and apartments </li>
<li>Good for snowboarders</li>
<li>A snowpark </li>
<li>Traditional restaurants </li>
<li>Great nightlife </li>
<li>Extras of ice rink, weekly market and cinema</li>
<li>Free lift passes for children under 8 years of age</li>
</ul>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/16c56b283bca4ae2b2ada820a5d3a03d" href="/{localLink:umb://document/16c56b283bca4ae2b2ada820a5d3a03d}" class="c-btn">View Val d'Isere</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h3 style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/996aa9008def4ffe9a331c775cc97902" href="/{localLink:umb://document/996aa9008def4ffe9a331c775cc97902}" title="Italy">Italy</a></h3>
<p><img src="/media/13062295/italy_the-dolomites-ski-area_selva_resort-view.jpg" alt="selvaitaly" data-udi="umb://media/b9d203825a95406e9bb29effe2e8a5dd" /></p>
<ul>
<li>A good selection of slopes with runs from blue to black</li>
<li>Ample nursery slopes near the village</li>
<li>Highly rated ski school </li>
<li>Selection of accommodation including ski-in ski-out</li>
<li>Wide, open pistes for snowboarders </li>
<li>Very picturesque villages in the area</li>
<li>Family activities including bowling and ice skating</li>
<li>Well known for it's designer shops, ideal for a shopping spree</li>
</ul>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/37d9070a8d4e4a609b9c192e453f0f97" href="/{localLink:umb://document/37d9070a8d4e4a609b9c192e453f0f97}" class="c-btn">View Selva</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h3 style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/7cc7c659d5214aa9b4d7bed936a721bb" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7cc7c659d5214aa9b4d7bed936a721bb}" title="Austria">Austria</a> </h3>
<p><img src="/media/13054044/austria_ellmau.jpg" alt="zelamsee" data-udi="umb://media/6141ed57b6fb4c598ad41f4e059a8f50" /></p>
<ul>
<li>Child safe with a pedestrianised town</li>
<li>A range of gentle slopes and good intermediate slopes </li>
<li>A selection of family ski areas and a fun park</li>
<li>Freestyle and terrain parks for avid snowboarders</li>
<li>Assortment of hotels </li>
<li>Great winter activities from ice skating to horse riding </li>
<li>A leisure centre with pool </li>
<li>Full programme of après ski events</li>
</ul>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/623c1118097f4c169108c9bc931e0af1" href="/{localLink:umb://document/623c1118097f4c169108c9bc931e0af1}" class="c-btn">View Zell am See</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<p> </p>
<h2>Best half-term accommodation:</h2>
<p>Here is a collection of some of our preferred half-term accommodation options.</p>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h3 style="text-align: center;">Salzburgerhof Hotel</h3>
<h3 style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/623c1118097f4c169108c9bc931e0af1" href="/{localLink:umb://document/623c1118097f4c169108c9bc931e0af1}" title="Zell am See">Zell am See</a></h3>
<p><img src="/media/13083264/wellness-garden-suite-min.jpg" alt="austriahotel" data-udi="umb://media/1ef7150190434090b62511ecc063c5ee" /></p>
<p>This 5* Hotel is perfect for families, with suites sleeping up to 4 and full-board dining options as well as a pool, your family will be fully catered for in all aspects along with top service. </p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/2060f4ca440844b29a57060cbf56d02e" href="/{localLink:umb://document/2060f4ca440844b29a57060cbf56d02e}" class="c-btn">View accommodation</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h3 style="text-align: center;">Soldanella Chalet</h3>
<h3 style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/37d9070a8d4e4a609b9c192e453f0f97" href="/{localLink:umb://document/37d9070a8d4e4a609b9c192e453f0f97}" title="Selva">Selva</a></h3>
<p><img src="/media/13094924/18-room-36-2nd-floor-se-facing.jpeg" alt="selvaitalyroom" data-udi="umb://media/88fa9949281647398c9c150724eb7d13" /></p>
<p>This 4* chalet is perfect for larger families or multiple families, with ample space and relaxing communal areas. It's only a short walk to the resort centre and the ski lifts. A welcoming atmosphere with great service.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/7097f7bf27624f9dbd07abc877b5a356" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7097f7bf27624f9dbd07abc877b5a356}" class="c-btn">View accommodation</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h3 style="text-align: center;">Hotel Ducs de Savoie</h3>
<h3 style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/16c56b283bca4ae2b2ada820a5d3a03d" href="/{localLink:umb://document/16c56b283bca4ae2b2ada820a5d3a03d}" title="Val d'Isere">Val d'Isere</a></h3>
<p><img src="/media/13088114/ducs-de-savoie-lounge.jpg" alt="valdiserehotel" data-udi="umb://media/33bee29f1c024d6bbe9bcd0e2283ef04" /></p>
<p>This hotel is family friendly and located in the resort centre so easy to get around. There is a children's club room within the hotel and offers free access to the local pool. </p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/a974436a181a43c193afabccefad916d" href="/{localLink:umb://document/a974436a181a43c193afabccefad916d}" class="c-btn">View accommodation</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h3 style="text-align: center;">Chalet Corniche</h3>
<h3 style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/204ce8e4cf8c4ab09205501e16cb7565" href="/{localLink:umb://document/204ce8e4cf8c4ab09205501e16cb7565}" title="Tignes">Tignes</a></h3>
<p><img src="/media/13094533/corniche-rooms-2-4-7-or-9-daytime.jpg" alt="tigneschlaet" data-udi="umb://media/f88b197237b94e92b1bf174dbffa01b5" /></p>
<p>This high-end, family equipped chalet is 150 metres to the resort centre and to the lifts. The chalet also includes a spacious living area with a wellness room for the adults to relax in.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/e611fe310a444e08a8b57c6b19dad7e4" href="/{localLink:umb://document/e611fe310a444e08a8b57c6b19dad7e4}" class="c-btn">View accommodation</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<p> </p>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-12">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h2>FAQ's for skiing holidays in Half-Term</h2>
<p><strong>What are the best resorts to visit with families?</strong> - On this page, we have selected some of the best options for resorts when skiing with your family, including younger children. Please also visit our <a data-udi="umb://document/a543e1407c404a978d9b4539252fc875" href="/{localLink:umb://document/a543e1407c404a978d9b4539252fc875}" title="Family Ski Holidays">Ski Holidays for Families</a> page for more resort options.</p>
<p><strong>What makes a ski resort good at half-term? </strong>The best thing about the ski resorts we have selected here is that we have checked for child-friendly slopes, nursery slopes, fun parks and ski schools. We have also selected resorts that offer other activities such as the cinema, bowling or ice skating, ensuring your family can have a fun filled week on and off the slopes. </p>
<p><strong>What accommodation would you recommend for half-term with a family?</strong> We have selected a range of hotels and chalets here and also on our <a data-udi="umb://document/a543e1407c404a978d9b4539252fc875" href="/{localLink:umb://document/a543e1407c404a978d9b4539252fc875}" title="Family Ski Holidays">Ski Holidays for Families</a> page that are child friendly, so you can feel at ease throughout your stay. Ideally you want to look for family friendly hotels, with larger rooms that can sleep up to 4 or 5 and possibly that offer additional facilities such as a pool or a games room. </p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h3 style="text-align: center;">When to go - <a data-udi="umb://document/93732bc5591f4b27b12da3503c02b7c3" href="/{localLink:umb://document/93732bc5591f4b27b12da3503c02b7c3}" title="April skiing">April</a></h3>
<p><img src="/media/13049028/kitz-ski.jpg" alt="togonovember" data-udi="umb://media/beb4b3d674f04407b7c7773d1bac02f5" /></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h3 style="text-align: center;">When to go - <a data-udi="umb://document/e160fd915c794359a9625dc3263f8ce8" href="/{localLink:umb://document/e160fd915c794359a9625dc3263f8ce8}" title="New Year Skiing">New Year</a></h3>
<p><img src="/media/13052690/09-salzburg-christmas-markets.jpg" alt="togochristmas" data-udi="umb://media/6312b7a440a743d893b01c72809f7cd5" /></p>
</div>
</div>
<p> </p>
